articles.title: It was a short stint for QB Daniel Jones in Minnesota. He reportedly plans to sign with the Colts. - Star Tribune
articles.description: Quarterback Daniel Jones' departure for a one-year, $14 million contract and a chance to compete for the Indianapolis starting job leaves the Vikings with just two QBs under contract.
articles.content:
It was a short stint for Daniel Jones in Minnesota.
